CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

June 9, 2006

[Cite as 06/09/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2870.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-0104. C.R. Green, L.P. v. Mayfield Hts.

Cuyahoga App. No. 85853, 2005-Ohio-6359. On appellant’s motion to clarify the court’s order of April 26, 2006, and appellee’s motion to dismiss the appeal. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed. Motion to clarify denied as moot.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
